      <title>JD Vance Pick 强化共和党转向保护主义贸易立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/jd-vance-pick-hardens-gop-swing-to-protectionist-trade-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周一选择参议员 JD Vance 作为其竞选搭档，此举进一步坚定了共和党向贸易保护主义转变的决心，也为未来数年巩固这一观点的继任者奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/jd-vance-pick-hardens-gop-swing-to-protectionist-trade-stance</guid>
